**WARNING MATURE AUDIENCES ONLY**  
Still here? That means you are old enough to talk SEX CRIMINALS, the hit comedy comic by Matt Fraction and Chip Zdarsky! Suzie, a [librarian](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Librarian "Librarian"), and Jon, an [actor](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Actor "Actor"), meet at a party and, after sleeping together, they discover that they share the ability to freeze time when they [orgasm](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orgasm "Orgasm"). As their relationship develops and their sexual histories are explored, they decide to rob the bank where Jon works in order to save Suzie's endangered library! It also turns out they aren't alone as they run afoul of the SEX POLICE!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience, and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
